Aardvark 2.2 for Moodle

UPDATES
-----------------------

CORE
- Change between fixed width (960px) and fluid/variable width (100%)
- Set background as centred, fixed or tiled
- Autohide for edit mode from Rocket theme now included

PROFILE BAR / HEADER
- Profile and header merged to create a twitter-style super bar
- Menu items only appear when logged in
- Icons updated
- Email icon only appears when set in Aardvark theme settings

BLOCKS
- Cleaner look to side blocks
- Today now shows highlighted in mini calendar

FOOTER
- Add copyright, disclaimer and social icons in Aardvark theme settings